polyp is obvious.
The or stage lasts thruout the winter,
and undergoes successive strobilization, an asexual reproduction
by transverse fission into ephyrae. A number of these tiny ephyrae
(larval jellyfishes) are liberated, and they gradually metamorphose
into the adult fenns.
